# Architecture

## Package Layout

```
src/gnc_enrich/
  cli.py            # CLI with run/review/apply subcommands, -v/--verbose flag
  config.py         # RunConfig, ApplyConfig, ReviewConfig, LlmConfig dataclasses
  domain/models.py  # Transaction, Split, Account, EmailEvidence, ReceiptEvidence, Proposal, ReviewDecision, etc.
  gnucash/loader.py # GnuCashLoader (gzip XML parse, filter), GnuCashWriter (backup, write, new account creation)
  email/parser.py   # EmlParser (stdlib email, SHA256 ID, GBP regex, full body)
  email/index.py    # EmailIndexRepository (JSONL index, recursive rglob, incremental)
  receipt/ocr.py    # ReceiptOcrEngine (Tesseract + optional LLM fallback)
  receipt/repository.py  # ReceiptRepository (list unprocessed, move to processed)
  matching/email_matcher.py   # Multi-signal scoring (amount, date, text)
  matching/receipt_matcher.py # One-to-one matching, amount tolerance
  ml/predictor.py   # CategoryPredictor (TF-IDF + SGDClassifier), FeedbackTrainer, evidence enrichment
  review/service.py # ReviewQueueService (queue, decisions, evidence-driven enrichment on submit)
  review/webapp.py  # Flask app with evidence approval checkboxes
  apply/engine.py   # ApplyEngine (dry-run, apply with backup/audit/journal, rollback)
  state/repository.py  # JSON/JSONL persistence with schema version headers
  services/pipeline.py # EnrichmentPipeline orchestrating all components
```

## Data Flow

`run` → load GnuCash → filter candidates → index emails → OCR receipts → match → predict → save proposals
`review` → Flask web app → one-by-one approval with evidence checkboxes → persist decisions
`apply` → load decisions → backup → write XML (descriptions + split accounts) → audit + journal
